org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.fxg.dom.text

Class BRNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.fxg.dom.AbstractFXGNode
      • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.fxg.dom.text.AbstractTextNode
        • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.fxg.dom.text.BRNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFXGNode, IPreserveWhiteSpaceNode, ITextNode

    public class BRNode
extends AbstractTextNode
    Represents a <br /> child tag of FXG <TextGraphic> content. A <br /> tag acts as a line separator for text content.

    This is an empty tag - text content or child tags are not expected.
